{
  "video_id": "257wV-AbKaE",
  "title": "How does money laundering work? - Delena D. Spann",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 11930.0,
      "end_time": 13984.0,
      "text": "As one of the most notorious gangsters in history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13984.0,
      "end_time": 19928.0,
      "text": "Al Capone presided over a vast and profitable empire of organized crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19928.0,
      "end_time": 21738.0,
      "text": "When he was finally put on trial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21738.0,
      "end_time": 26363.0,
      "text": "the most he could be convicted of was tax evasion."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26363.0,
      "end_time": 28604.0,
      "text": "The nearly $100 million a year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28604.0,
      "end_time": 32308.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s 1.4 billion in today&#39;s currency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32308.0,
      "end_time": 34737.0,
      "text": "that Capone had earned from illegal gambling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34737.0,
      "end_time": 35898.0,
      "text": "bootlegging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35898.0,
      "end_time": 37450.0,
      "text": "brothels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37450.0,
      "end_time": 38412.0,
      "text": "and extortion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38412.0,
      "end_time": 41317.0,
      "text": "would have served as evidence of his crimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41317.0,
      "end_time": 44985.0,
      "text": "But the money was nowhere to be found."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44985.0,
      "end_time": 49265.0,
      "text": "Capone and his associates had hidden it through investments in various businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49265.0,
      "end_time": 52736.0,
      "text": "whose ultimate ownership couldn&#39;t be proven,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52736.0,
      "end_time": 55474.0,
      "text": "like cash-only laundromats."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55474.0,
      "end_time": 60605.0,
      "text": "In fact, those laundromats are part of the reason for the name of this activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60605.0,
      "end_time": 62995.0,
      "text": "money laundering."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62995.0,
      "end_time": 66235.0,
      "text": "Money laundering came  to be the term for any process"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66235.0,
      "end_time": 72185.0,
      "text": "that cleans illegally obtained funds of their dirty criminal origins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72185.0,
      "end_time": 76516.0,
      "text": "allowing them to be used within the legal economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76516.0,
      "end_time": 80375.0,
      "text": "But Capone wasn&#39;t the first to launder money."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80375.0,
      "end_time": 84606.0,
      "text": "In fact, this practice is about as old as money itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84606.0,
      "end_time": 87536.0,
      "text": "Merchants hid their riches from tax collecters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87536.0,
      "end_time": 91746.0,
      "text": "and pirates sought to sell their bounty without drawing attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91746.0,
      "end_time": 93836.0,
      "text": "to how they got it."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93836.0,
      "end_time": 96960.0,
      "text": "With the recent arrival  of virtual currencies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96960.0,
      "end_time": 97766.0,
      "text": "offshore banking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97766.0,
      "end_time": 99467.0,
      "text": "the darknet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 99467.0,
      "end_time": 101136.0,
      "text": "and global markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101136.0,
      "end_time": 104607.0,
      "text": "schemes have become much more complex."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104607.0,
      "end_time": 107876.0,
      "text": "Although modern money laundering methods vary greatly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107876.0,
      "end_time": 110836.0,
      "text": "most share three basic steps:"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110836.0,
      "end_time": 111948.0,
      "text": "placement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111948.0,
      "end_time": 113137.0,
      "text": "layering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113138.0,
      "end_time": 115476.0,
      "text": "and integration."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115476.0,
      "end_time": 120337.0,
      "text": "Placement is where illegally obtained money is converted into assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120337.0,
      "end_time": 122366.0,
      "text": "that seem legitimate."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122366.0,
      "end_time": 125656.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s often done by depositing funds into a bank account"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125656.0,
      "end_time": 131737.0,
      "text": "registered to an anonymous corporation or a professional middleman."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131737.0,
      "end_time": 135400.0,
      "text": "This step is where criminals are often most vulnerable to detection"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135400.0,
      "end_time": 138967.0,
      "text": "since they introduce massive wealth into the financial system"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138967.0,
      "end_time": 141899.0,
      "text": "seemingly out of nowhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141899.0,
      "end_time": 146278.0,
      "text": "The second step, layering, involves using multiple transactions"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146278.0,
      "end_time": 150660.0,
      "text": "to further distance the funds from their origin."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150670.0,
      "end_time": 153127.0,
      "text": "This can take the form of transfers between multiple accounts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153127.0,
      "end_time": 155758.0,
      "text": "or the purchase of tradable property,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155758.0,
      "end_time": 157428.0,
      "text": "like expensive cars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 157428.0,
      "end_time": 158303.0,
      "text": "artwork,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 158303.0,
      "end_time": 159917.0,
      "text": "and real estate."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 159917.0,
      "end_time": 163780.0,
      "text": "Casinos, where large sums of money change hands every second,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 163780.0,
      "end_time": 167208.0,
      "text": "are also popular venues for layering."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167208.0,
      "end_time": 170609.0,
      "text": "A money launderer may have their gambling balance made available"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 170609.0,
      "end_time": 173960.0,
      "text": "at a casino chain&#39;s locations  in other countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 173960.0,
      "end_time": 177709.0,
      "text": "or work with employees to rig games."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177709.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "The last step, integration, allows clean money to re-enter the mainstream economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 186590.0,
      "text": "and to benefit the original criminal."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 186590.0,
      "end_time": 188669.0,
      "text": "They might invest it into a legal business"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 188669.0,
      "end_time": 191309.0,
      "text": "claiming payment by producing fake invoices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 191309.0,
      "end_time": 193950.0,
      "text": "or even start a bogus charity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 193950.0,
      "end_time": 196489.0,
      "text": "placing themselves  on the board of directors"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 196490.0,
      "end_time": 199370.0,
      "text": "with an exorbitant salary."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 199370.0,
      "end_time": 200689.0,
      "text": "Money laundering itself"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 200689.0,
      "end_time": 206950.0,
      "text": "wasn&#39;t officially recognized as a federal crime in the United States until 1986."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 206950.0,
      "end_time": 210730.0,
      "text": "Before that point, the government needed to prosecute a related crime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 210730.0,
      "end_time": 213679.0,
      "text": "like tax evasion."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 213680.0,
      "end_time": 217840.0,
      "text": ">From 1986 on, they could confiscate wealth simply by demonstrating"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 217840.0,
      "end_time": 220610.0,
      "text": "that concealment had occurred,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 220610.0,
      "end_time": 224570.0,
      "text": "which had a positive effect on prosecuting major criminal operations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 224570.0,
      "end_time": 226880.0,
      "text": "like drug traffickers."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 226880.0,
      "end_time": 229900.0,
      "text": "However, a legal shift has raised concerns"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 229901.0,
      "end_time": 233931.0,
      "text": "involving privacy  and government surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 233931.0,
      "end_time": 235852.0,
      "text": "Today, the United Nations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 235852.0,
      "end_time": 237411.0,
      "text": "national governments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 237411.0,
      "end_time": 238992.0,
      "text": "and various nonprofits"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 238992.0,
      "end_time": 240932.0,
      "text": "fight against money laundering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 240932.0,
      "end_time": 246300.0,
      "text": "yet the practice continues to play a major role in global crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 246310.0,
      "end_time": 248816.0,
      "text": "And the most high-profile instances of money laundering"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 248816.0,
      "end_time": 251803.0,
      "text": "have involved  not just private individuals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 251803.0,
      "end_time": 257207.0,
      "text": "but major financial institutions and government officials."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 257207.0,
      "end_time": 260101.0,
      "text": "No one knows for sure the total amount of money"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 260101.0,
      "end_time": 262832.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s laundered on a yearly basis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 262833.0,
      "end_time": 269736.0,
      "text": "but some organizations estimate it to be in the hundreds of billions of dollars."
    }
  ]
}